speed benchmark for karpathy's microgpt. a minimal gpt trained on tiny shakespeare,
one forward + backward pass per step. ref: https://karpathy.github.io/2026/02/12/microgpt/

to submit: add a .py file prefixed with your username and open a pr.
one rule: any python library is welcome, but no inline c.

